&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuously improve model quality:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor, test, and iterate on model accuracy, robustness, privacy, and safety within live clinical workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contribute across the product:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate across the stack—from APIs and backend systems to product UX and workflow design—to deliver cohesive, AI-driven features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
